The flutter_gpu_texture_renderer plugin ships only a placeholder upstream
LICENSE, so avoid resolving and embedding it.  It is unused on Linux anyway:
the GPU texture renderer supports only Windows, guarded by the vram Cargo
feature that this ebuild does not enable.

